                "img": "https://arxiv.org/html/2602.20672/figures/refine/images/zebra_1.jpeg",
                "caption": "Figure 3:Disentangled parametric refinement via structured re-generation.Each example starts from an image generated from a structured JSON prompt. We then edit only the relevant JSON fields and re-generate using the same random seed. Although the model does not observe the original image, it produces localized changes that follow the modified parameters while preserving the rest of the scene, demonstrating strong parametric disentanglement. Ground-truth bounding boxes are overlaid for visualization.",
